name: Delicious Garlic Baguette
desc: Sliced baguette. It is said that every now and then, the people of Fontaine organize baking competitions. The bakers who make the best baguette get to show off their skills in the Palais Mermonia. This baguette could definitely win first prize in those competitions!

customize.name: Recipe: Garlic Baguette
customize.desc: A detailed step-by-step recipe for making a Garlic Baguette.

customize.name: Flour
customize.desc: A powder ground from wheat. No matter what it goes into, it brings a sense of satisfaction to the diner.

customize.name: Butter
customize.desc: An extract from milk. With the appropriate application, it can bring rich aromas to even the most basic ingredients.

customize.name: Garlic Baguette
customize.desc: Sliced baguette. Taken freshly out of the oven, the bread has a crispy, crackling crust, and soft, fluffy crumb. The aroma of butter and garlic further adds to the baguette's tastiness! No wonder you often see Fontainians buying a baguette on their way home after work.

customize.name: Suspicious Garlic Baguette
customize.desc: Sliced baguette. It is so hard that one can't help but look at the plate and wonder: Is this baguette a stone in disguise?

value.text: Increase all party members' ATK by 95 for 300s. In Co-Op Mode, this effect only applies to your own character(s).
